description.plain: Montell Fish, a 22 year old Christian creative, is passionate about making music/art and glorifying God through it. He’s released 12 projects over the past few years, his latest Camp Lukewarm. In early 2019, He launched his brand/label Lord’s Child Worldwide along with his manager and ministry partner Patrick Bradley. Fish is also known for making videos on his YouTube platform. Montell Fish embraces unique and original sounding music with an attitude of humility, love, and worship to the Lord from a child’s heart. Montell Fish and Lord’s Child continue to tour with other Christian creatives and musicians. Be on the lookout for more music from the label, new merch, and stay up to date on Montell Fish, Patrick Bradley, and Lord’s Child.

songs.title: Hotel

description.plain: Hotel is the debut single off Montell Fish’s 2022 EP, Her Love Haunts Me Like a Ghost. Hotel was released on September 15th after Montell Fish teased it on TikTok and SoundCloud over the summer of 2022, and it explores the regret yet also yearning of a night spent with a girl in a hotel room.
